---
const title = "AI Recipes Hub";
const subtitle = "Готовые рецепты для маркетинга, автоматизаций и креатива.";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-30 blur-3xl"
       style="background: radial-gradient(60% 60% at 50% 20%, #a78bfa 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(40% 40% at 80% 60%, #22d3ee 0%, transparent 60%);">
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pt-14 pb-12 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight animate-fadein">
      AssortiAI — <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">{title}</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-600 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fadein" style="animation-delay:.06s;">
      {subtitle}
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 animate-fadein" style="animation-delay:.12s;">
      <a href="/recipes/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl bg-black text-white hover:opacity-90 transition">Смотреть рецепты</a>
      <a href="https://t.me/aiprofithub" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-zinc-300 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition">AI Profit Hub</a>
    </div>

    <div id="get-started" class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-left">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">1. Выбери рецепт</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-600 mt-1">Категории: video, text, automation...</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">2. Следуй шагам</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-600 mt-1">Готовые промпты и инструменты.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">3. Публикуй результат</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-600 mt-1">OG-картинки и превью для соцсетей.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@keyframes fadein { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px) } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) } }
.animate-fadein { animation: fadein .5s ease both; }
</style>
